GLSL Samplers
Programming

<p>This is the result of the rendering algorithms course of FS09 at UniBE.</p>

<p>We built a ray tracer with standard features. In the image you can see the following features:
<ul>
 	<li>Perlin Noise Texturen</li>
 	<li>Bump Mapping</li>
 	<li>Depth of Field</li>
 	<li>Refraction</li>
 	<li>Environment Mapping</li>
 	<li>Photon Mapping (Caustics)</li>
</ul>
</p>

